Just a technique of what we do.

15:43.469 --> 15:46.604
Just shaping it so it fits, it stacks.

15:46.705 --> 15:51.809
It's not clay, it's meat.

15:51.910 --> 15:54.144
The chicken and sausage gumbo... bland.

15:54.246 --> 15:56.346
But do you know what?

15:56.447 --> 15:57.547
Forget the seasoning.

15:57.648 --> 15:58.749
It wasn't even hot. It was lukewarm.

15:58.850 --> 16:00.350
I sent it out as soon as I did it.

16:00.451 --> 16:02.519
